string-array.item: We believe in Jesus because he is our salvation from our sins. He is the only one that paid the price for us to escape the eternal damnation from our sins. We have various church values that are connected to our church. Some of the key values are: praise, worship, ministry and love. Ministry is the work and opportunity that God allows us to partake in pertaining to his kingdom. Ministry is important because it allows us to overcome our legacy, the negative from our past and ourselves that would have produced bad fruit in our futures. Ministry helps us produce good spiritually and naturally as we move forward in our lives.
